{"tid":1358481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嬲呀嬲呀好嬲呀 咁文宣呢？","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:27:57.000Z","uid":47509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65dffa1ab3ffd6841f4ac492fcf9d6528ae5cf3b","tid":1358481,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"自從721之後文宣真係退步左小小<br />\n港鐵 黎緊既機場 元朗都未有實質好大既宣傳<br />\n<br />\n我覺得大家都要明白<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過住既所有重要日子 都有強大既文宣去支撐住 所擔當既角色重要 </span><br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理 文宣 呢3樣野本身就係我地一開始既根基<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d22b03892dbd0a5c39e69261efd619dd073e157","tid":1358481,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"62704b03b2aaab200955b3595ddb2719179d1b76","tid":1358481,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba58bb1b3cb3f0da407a9e1b1ab341178d53bb3","tid":1358481,"uid":47509,"like